        <!-- Section 1: Emergency Procedures -->
        <section>
            <h2>Emergency Procedures</h2>
            <p>
                In case of an emergency, follow the procedures outlined below:
            </p>
            <ol>
                <li>Stay calm and assess the situation.</li>
                <li>Find the nearest emergency exit and evacuate the area if necessary.</li>
                <li>Do not use elevators during emergencies.</li>
                <li>Follow instructions from emergency personnel.</li>
            </ol>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 2: Emergency Alert Button -->
        <section>
            <h2>Initiate Emergency Alert</h2>
            <p>
                If you are in immediate danger and need assistance, click the button below to send an emergency alert to college members.
